   [Brown-Guedira, G.] N Carolina State Univ, USDA ARS, Eastern Reg Genotyping Lab, Raleigh, NC 27695 USA.
   [Jin, Y.] Univ Minnesota, USDA ARS, Cereal Dis Lab, St Paul, MN 55108 USA.
