   [Tyrrell, Simon; Bian, Xingdong; Davey, Robert P.] Norwich Res Pk, Genome Anal Ctr TGAC, Norwich, Norfolk, England.
   [Caccamo, Mario] NIAB, Huntingdon Rd, Cambridge, England.
