   [Shah, S. Jawad A.] NIFA, Crop Breeding Div, Plant Pathol Grp, Peshawar, Pakistan.
   [Rahman, Hidayatur] NW Frontier Prov Agr Univ, Dept Plant Breeding & Genet, Peshawar, Pakistan.
