   [Bhat, Prasanna R.; Close, Timothy J.] Univ Calif Riverside, Dep Bot & Plant Sci, Riverside, CA 92521 USA.
   [Chao, Shiaoman] USDA ARS, Fargo, ND 58105 USA.
