   [Ma, Hongxiang] JAAS, Inst Plant Genet & Biotechnol, Nanjing, Peoples R China.
   [Ma, Hongxiang; Hu, Shengwa] Kansas State Univ, Dept Agron, Manhattan, KS 66506 USA.
